  <brief_title>MDA D-Dimer / Recurrent DVT Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Cohort Study Evaluating the Safety of a Diagnostic Strategy Involving D-Dimer and Compression Ultrasonography in Patients With Suspected Recurrent Deep Vein Thrombosis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
